        <div class="gap-2 mb-8">
          <p class="">
            <span class="text-b-willow-dark">Nairobi-based </span>
            designer fluent in both design and code.
          </p>
          <p>
            I specialize in untangling complex B2B systems—transforming them into intuitive products that users love and businesses rely on, delivered on time and on budget.
          </p>
        </div>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-5">
